        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(ui): harden publisher profile and skill/plugin detail polish",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nDetail-hardening pass across publisher profiles, skill/plugin detail pages, and browse flows. No new product surfaces — focused on layout stability, mobile polish, broken states, and filter UX.\n\n### Publisher profile\n- Polish publisher detail hero, catalog grouping, members UI, and chrome layout\n- Default catalog tab, plugin links, and visual proof updates\n- Avatar/badge detail fixes and e2e stabilization for profile catalog flows\n\n### Skill & plugin detail\n- **Diff tab:** bundle Monaco locally and show a real skeleton while the diff viewer loads (fixes stuck “Loading diff…”)\n- **Versions table:** separate grid column layouts for skills vs plugins\n- **Hero summary:** inline `` `code` `` contrast in light mode via `InlineCodeSummary`\n- **Topic links:** skill hero topics link into browse; malformed `?topic%3Dgithub` URLs are parsed and canonicalized\n- **Install card:** ghost icon-only copy button, vertical centering on CLI, top-right on Prompt, no tab-switch whip; mobile Prompt text wrap fix\n- **Mobile hero:** Star moves to creator row (right-aligned); install card spacing above creator block\n- **Files panel:** loading skeleton and min-height while fetching\n- **Creator badge:** subtle hover on skill hero creator row\n\n### Browse & search\n- Active topic chip with clear (×) on skills/plugins browse\n- `useBrowseTopicSearch` hook + `browseTopicSearch` helpers for URL sanitization\n- Navbar typeahead searching state matches empty-state layout (spinner + label)\n\n### Tests & CI\n- Restored category helper coverage alongside new topic browse tests\n- Router test mocks updated for `useRouterState` in browse hooks\n- Diff card loading skeleton uses shared `Skeleton` component\n\n## Test plan\n- [ ] Skill detail mobile: creator + Star row, Install card spacing, CLI/Prompt copy alignment\n- [ ] Skill detail: Diff tab loads Monaco and shows skeleton first\n- [ ] `/skills?topic=github` shows active chip with ×; malformed topic URLs canonicalize\n- [ ] Versions tables on skill and plugin detail use correct columns\n- [ ] Navbar search: empty and searching states look consistent\n- [ ] Publisher profile catalog tabs and mobile layout",
